gomodel:SYNGO_3130  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: [Fig.1: \"Progranulin from PCs Counteracts CF Synapse Elimination from P11 to P16\"]\n\n[Fig.2: \"Progranulin in PCs Reinforces the Strongest CFs, Promotes Their Extension along PC Dendrites, and Contributes to Normal Gait\"]\n\nFig.4: \"Sort1 in CFs Mediates the Effect of Progranulin on CF Synapse Elimination\". Experimental description: - \" Sample traces of CF-EPSC (B) and frequency distributions of the number of CFs innervating each PC examined during P12 to P14 for control (white columns, 3 mice) and Sort1 knockdown (Sort1-KD) (magenta columns, 3 mice)\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
